lead_paragraph: The World Health Organization on Wednesday reported the lowest weekly total of new Ebola cases so far this year in the three nations of West Africa that have been afflicted by the deadly virus.

headline.main: Health Agency Reports Lowest Weekly Total of New Ebola Cases
headline.print_headline: Health Agency Reports Lowest Weekly Total of New Ebola Cases
